OL,5, The clearance of payments considered to
OL,6, be risky should be slowed down to      
OL,7, tackle the "epidemic" of fraud, says   
OL,8, Nationwide's economic crime director.  
OL,10,FStuart Skinner said there should be    
OL,11,Fmore "friction" in the payments system 
OL,12,Fto prevent money getting into          
OL,13,Ffraudsters' hands.                     
OL,15,FThe move would require an overhaul of  
OL,16,Fthe UK's payments system which is      
OL,17,Fdesigned for customer convenience.     
OL,19,FHis comments come as Nationwide        
OL,20,Flaunches a new fraud checking hotline. 
